    ubuntu搭建jenkins

    # 01、安装jdk

    执行sudo apt-get install openjdk-11-jdk,安装完成后查看jdk版本java -version

    # 02.安装存储秘钥

    执行wget -q -O - https://pkg.jenkins.io/debian-stable/jenkins.io.key | sudo apt-key add -

    # 03、添加镜像源

    执行sudo sh -c 'echo deb https://pkg.jenkins.io/debian-stable binary/ > /etc/apt/sources.list.d/jenkins.list'

    # 04、更新镜像源

    执行sudo apt-get update

    # 05、安装jenkins

    执行apt-get install jenkins

    # 06、启动jenkins

    执行sudo systemctl start jenkins

    # 07、查看jenkins状态

    执行sudo systemctl status jenkins

    # 08、访问jenkins

    浏览器中输入http://192.168.1.1:8080

    # 09、获取初始密码

    执行sudo cat /var/lib/jenkins/secrets/initialAdminPassword
